Subject: [PATCH] remoteproc: imx_dsp_rproc: Add custom memory copy
 implementation for i.MX DSP Cores
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 6.1.30
Git-commit: 408ec1ff0caa340c57eecf4cbd14ef0132036a50

[ Upstream commit 408ec1ff0caa340c57eecf4cbd14ef0132036a50 ]

The IRAM is part of the HiFi DSP.
According to hardware specification only 32-bits write are allowed
otherwise we get a Kernel panic.

Therefore add a custom memory copy and memset functions to deal with
the above restriction.

